title: "CBO Brother, Where Art Thou?"
description: Tommy and Jon discuss the ongoing efforts to ram Trumpcare through the Senate, and whether Obama did enough to respond to and deter Russian interference in our election. Then they discuss the impact of Trumpcare on West Virginia with Senator Joe Manchin.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
